features: 【Multiple Capacity Options】: Say goodbye to storage limitations with the Somnambulist H650 Black Dragon SSD, offering a range of capacities to suit your needs. Choose from 120GB, 240GB, 480GB, 1TB, or indulge in a massive 2TB variant.Whether you're a professional handling large media files or seeking seamless multitasking for everyday tasks, this SSD has the perfect capacity for you

【Excellent Performance】: Experience blazing-fast speeds with the Somnambulist H650 Black Dragon SSD. With read and write speeds of up to 550MB/s and 450MB/s respectively, this SATA SSD ensures your computer performs at its peak. Please note that the transmission speed may vary based on the capacity, hardware, test software, and operating system

【Super Compatibility】: The Somnambulist H650 Black Dragon SSD is engineered to seamlessly integrate into your system. Its 2.5-inch 7mm (0.28-inch) size and SATA 3 6Gb/s interface guarantee compatibility with a wide range of desktop and notebook computers in the market. Rest assured, we format the SSD with NTFS for optimal performance

【Capacity Algorithm】: Transparency is our priority at Somnambulist. Our SSD utilizes a decimal algorithm, where 1MB equals 1000KB and 1GB equals 1000MB. However, operating systems use a binary algorithm, recognizing 1MB as 1024KB and 1GB as 1024MB. As a result, there might be a slight difference between the nominal capacity and the actual capacity of the SSD

【Long-Term Reliability】: We stand behind the H650 Black Dragon SSD's quality and reliability with utmost confidence. Hence, we offer an extended three-year warranty. This warranty ensures that you can use your SSD with peace of mind, knowing that it's built to last and backed by our commitment to customer satisfaction

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Product, Better Warranty Service
reviews.reviewText: I purchased several of these drives for my "home lab" computers because they offered good performance/size for an excellent price - and I figured I would test them out since my intended use was not "mission critical." I installed both drives in different machines and while one is still working great, the other started failing with unrecoverable bad blocks at about the 3 month point. (Infant mortality happens with all drives, so that's not unexpected from time to time.) However, what really surprised and impressed me was the professional and exceptional way the manufacturer/seller responded to my warranty request. I received a new replacement drive in less than a week after providing reasonable proof of the failure. I couldn't be happier. I would definitely purchased this drive (or others like it) again - knowing that the manufacturer/seller actually stands behind it and honors their warranty! Kudos deserved - Well done!

reviews.reviewText: This arrived quickly, was a great price and lower than others with this capacity. I purchased it for a Eufy Home Base 3 security unit to expand it's storage and it went in super easy. The SDD was recognized immediately, and I opted to have the Eufy device reformat it for use to further ensure it was good, but no issues. It's also a good looking case enclosure with nothing exposed if you plan to use an external cable kit and as you will not need purchase a protective case. It weighs hardly anything so also great for on the go!

O Somnambulist SSD 1TB SATA III apresenta-se como um dispositivo de armazenamento de inquestionável excelência, digno de figurar entre os primorosos equipamentos tecnológicos de nossa era. Com uma capacidade volumosa de 1 Terabyte, este sofisticado SSD concede aos usuários a possibilidade de armazenar, com destreza e eficiência, uma plêiade de dados, desde documentos profissionais até preciosos momentos familiares em formato de imagens e vídeos.A inovadora tecnologia SATA III, que permeia o cerne deste aparelho, garante uma transferência de dados veloz e ininterrupta, proporcionando aos usuários uma experiência fluida e imperturbável. Este modelo transcende as limitações de seus predecessores, elevando-se como um verdadeiro paradigma de rapidez e confiabilidade no segmento de armazenamento digital.Destarte, o Somnambulist SSD 1TB SATA III revela-se como uma opção de notável qualidade e requinte, destinado aos que prezam por um equipamento com desempenho ímpar e design elegante. É, indubitavelmente, um investimento meritório para os ávidos por soluções inovadoras e eficazes no vasto domínio da tecnologia.

O produto chegou dentro do prazo, está funcionando bem, gostei muito pela velocidade de inicialização do computador, muito rápido. Indico este produto para pessoas querem melhorar o desempenho de computadores antigos, vale a pena pelo custo benefício.

reviews.reviewTitle: Tiene las 3B Bueno, Bonito y Barato
reviews.reviewText: Lo que me agradó fue que no tuviese que formatearlo para instalar Windows, reviví un portátil de hace 10 años con este pequeñin, si buscas este ssd para un armado más enfocado para Gaming es buenísimo, para probar esta marca compré el ejemplar de 120GBPero lo recomiendo en todas sus presentaciones.

Produto corresponde pelo valor pago. É rapido, mas não se compara com os produtos mais caros que na sua construção leva mais componentes importantes para auxiliar no desempenho.Usei para construir minha Steam Machine e funciona perfeitamente bem.Tenho um SSD em outro computador da mesma marca , há mais de 2 anos funcionando perfeitamente. Isso mostr que sua durabilidade é razoável.A entrega foi super rápida, cerca de 10 dias depois de efetuar a compra.Se quiser dar aquele upgrade no seu pc ou notebook, está aí o produto.
